data.description: Must see year round home with 171 feet of shoreline on Crystal lake. This updated three bedroom, two bath home has an open concept kitchen and dining room, two fireplaces and ample storage inside the home, as well as in the three stall heated garage. The large private master suite boasts a seating area and a cozy fireplace, with views all around. A private level lot, large lakeside deck, fire pit area and patio off the garage complete this move in ready package. The seller has also added a new heating and cooling system in the home and garage.
